  "Description": {
    "English": "A living, fertile egg, <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">ready to hatch!</span><br><br>The delicate creature within flutters its layered wings, longing to be free.<br><br>Scans indicate the being within has the genetic potential for a <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">devoted</span> companion, happiest when flying close to its master.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一枚有生命的、可孵化的卵，<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">已经准备好孵化！</span><br><br>寄宿其中的柔弱生物正扑扇着自己的多层翅膀，渴望能够自由飞行。<br><br>根据扫描结果显示，里面的生物拥有<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">热忱</span>的基因潜质，最喜欢在自己的主人身边飞翔。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "有生命、可孵化的蛋，<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">且即將孵化！</span><br><br>裡面的嬌貴生物拍打著多層的翅膀，渴望自由。<br><br>掃描結果顯示，該生物可能擁有以下形容的大小及特徵：是<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">忠心</span>的同伴，在主人身旁飛行就是牠最開心的時刻。"
  },
